channel.description:
Difficulty : 1/10
Tested On: DeltaScape

First Start Off By Opening NPCHANDLER.java

Search: 					[code]if (npcs[i].RandomWalk == true) {[/code]

You will see something like this:

[code]					if (npcs[i].RandomWalk == true) {
						npcs[i].getNextNPCMovement();
					}[/code]

Under that last bracket Paste this Code: 

[code] if (npcs[i].npcType == NPC you want) {
                        if (misc.random2(15) <= 3)
                        {
                            npcs[i].updateRequired = true;
                            npcs[i].animUpdateRequired = true;
                                npcs[i].animNumber = emote you want the npc to do;
                            }
                        }[/code]

The misc.random2(15) <= 3) is how fast you want the emote to perform again.

Hope it helps some people.
